reviewText: One of the most amazing DVDs I've ever watched. The science and story will take your breath away. If you struggle with doubt, this DVD and the science behind it will alleviate it.
Amazing and inspiring! A must see video...

This Dvd was given to my husband while we were walking out of adoration at our parish one day a month ago. It is awesome. Tim Francis has so much charisma and is a great speaker too! Learning about these miracles and the stigmata make you feel so on fire about your faith. Great for lukewarm Catholics! The website loveandmercy.org has other great resources from the messages to Catalina from Jesus that I highly recommend. Especially the writings on the Holy Mass. Life-changing. Buy it, you won't regret it!! Then share it with others!!!
Changed the way I think and act as a Roman Catholic.  I am buying one for all my family to spread the message.  I highly recommend to everyone!!!
